casebody.data:
Robert Lee THACKER
v.
STATE of North Carolina. No. 351P04. Supreme Court of North Carolina. October 11, 2004. Robert Lee Thacker, Pro Se. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, R. Stuart Albright, District Attorney, for State.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Plaintiff on the 30th day of June 2004 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Guilford County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 6th day of October 2004."
